{"nodes": [{"type": "text", "id": "ec36f8e99cbe46b1", "x": 0, "y": -200, "width": 2400, "height": 110, "color": "6", "text": "# 988 \u5eda\u623f B2B \u88dc\u8ca8\u7cfb\u7d71\u67b6\u69cb\n*LIFF \u8a02\u55ae \u2192 Supabase \u2192 n8n \u2192 Google Sheet + LINE OA \u4e09\u5c64\u67b6\u69cb (2026-04-20 \u5f8c\u5be6\u6cc1)*"}, {"type": "text", "id": "f2c332b4e1334e1c", "x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 540, "height": 220, "color": "4", "text": "\u2699\ufe0f ## LIFF \u88dc\u8ca8 App\n*Vite + React + TS*\n\nDesktop/988-kitchen\nVercel auto-deploy"}, {"type": "text", "id": "3912864296074dce", "x": 700, "y": 0, "width": 540, "height": 220, "color": "4", "text": "\u2699\ufe0f ## LINE Messaging API\n*988 \u5eda\u623f\u5b98\u65b9\u5e33\u865f*\n\nLIFF login + \u63a8\u64ad\u8f09\u9ad4"}, {"type": "text", "id": "eed41d1d66544f62", "x": 1400, "y": 0, "width": 540, "height": 220, "color": "4", "text": "\u2699\ufe0f ## CRM \u5f8c\u53f0\n*Next.js + Tailwind*\n\n988-kitchen/988-admin\n\u5546\u54c1 / \u8a02\u55ae / \u63a8\u85a6 / \u7bc4\u672c"}, {"type": "text", "id": "8251523d04294e3b", "x": 0, "y": 360, "width": 540, "height": 220, "color": "5", "text": "\u2699\ufe0f ## Edge Function api-988\n*Deno + Hono + 12 endpoints*\n\n\u670d\u52d9 LIFF + CRM + \u88dc\u9001\n\u5beb\u5165 + n8n webhook \u89f8\u767c"}, {"type": "text", "id": "46bd22edd4cb4e3c", "x": 700, "y": 360, "width": 540, "height": 220, "color": "5", "text": "\u2699\ufe0f ## Postgres (Supabase)\n*orders / customers / products*\n*promotions / templates*\n\nRLS + service role only"}, {"type": "text", "id": "1f49f2acdba645a9", "x": 1400, "y": 360, "width": 540, "height": 220, "color": "3", "text": "\u2699\ufe0f ## Schedule \u88dc\u9001\n*\u6bcf 10 \u5206 (Mac Mini)*\n*\u6bcf\u6574\u9ede (MacBook \u96d9\u4fdd\u96aa)*\n\nPOST /retry-pending-orders\nn8n_notified=false \u6488\u51fa"}, {"type": "text", "id": "dcdffab941b94f35", "x": 0, "y": 720, "width": 540, "height": 220, "color": "5", "text": "\u2699\ufe0f ## ngrok \u56fa\u5b9a\u57df\u540d\n*lexicographic-unspoilt-stephine*\n\nEdge Function \u2192 n8n webhook\nx-webhook-secret \u9a57\u8b49"}, {"type": "text", "id": "f01ecfb049884cc4", "x": 700, "y": 720, "width": 540, "height": 220, "color": "5", "text": "\u2699\ufe0f ## Cloudflare Tunnel\n*n8n.vjvan.com*\n\n\u7ba1\u7406 UI \u5c0d\u5916\u5b58\u53d6\ncloudflared \u5bb9\u5668"}, {"type": "text", "id": "543d4d754cbf4ebf", "x": 0, "y": 1080, "width": 540, "height": 220, "color": "6", "text": "\u2699\ufe0f ## n8n on Mac Mini\n*compose: minimal-postgres*\n*v2.16.1 / Publish + Active*\n\nWorkflow: B2B 988 Order\n+ Error Workflow + Schedule"}, {"type": "text", "id": "ee9f6e516e7645f3", "x": 700, "y": 1080, "width": 540, "height": 220, "color": "6", "text": "\u2699\ufe0f ## n8n Postgres 17\n*workflows / credentials*\n*executions*\n\n\u672c\u6a5f docker volume\n\u5099\u4efd: ~/backups/n8n-988-*"}, {"type": "text", "id": "43e030dd8ee145b2", "x": 0, "y": 1440, "width": 540, "height": 220, "color": "6", "text": "\u2699\ufe0f ## Google Sheet ERP\n*ERP_Import_Flat*\n\n\u8a02\u55ae\u6241\u5e73\u5316\u5beb\u5165\n\u5f8c\u53f0 ERP key \u55ae\u4f86\u6e90"}, {"type": "text", "id": "1b824ede0e5d4129", "x": 700, "y": 1440, "width": 540, "height": 220, "color": "6", "text": "\u2699\ufe0f ## LINE \u63a8\u64ad\n*\u5ba2\u6236\u78ba\u8a8d + \u5167\u90e8\u901a\u77e5*\n\n\ud83d\udce6 admin (\u8a73\u7d30)\n\u2705 customer (\u53cb\u5584)\n\u4e0b\u55ae\u4eba always \u6536 customer"}, {"type": "text", "id": "b8d32ef9d53d4f7a", "x": 2500, "y": 0, "width": 400, "height": 300, "color": "1", "text": "## \u914d\u8272\u8a9e\u610f\n\n\ud83d\udfe2 4 \u7da0 = \u5ba2\u6236/\u54e1\u5de5\u5074 + happy path\n\ud83d\udd35 5 \u9752 = Supabase \u670d\u52d9 + \u901a\u9053\n\ud83d\udfe3 6 \u7d2b = Mac Mini \u5f8c\u7aef + \u4e0b\u6e38\n\ud83d\udfe1 3 \u9ec3 = \u88dc\u9001 / \u964d\u7d1a\u4fdd\u96aa\n\n## \u4e09\u5c64\u4fdd\u96aa\n1. Mac Mini \u5373\u6642 webhook\n2. Mac Mini Schedule \u6bcf 10 \u5206\u88dc\u9001\n3. MacBook Schedule \u6bcf\u6574\u9ede\u88dc\u9001\n\n## \u96d9\u901a\u9053\u7406\u7531\n- ngrok: Edge \u2192 n8n (\u6a5f\u5668\u5c0d\u6a5f\u5668)\n- CF Tunnel: \u5141\u96f7\u7ba1\u7406 UI \u5165\u53e3\n\n## \u5df2\u77e5\u7f3a\u53e3\n- webhook 200 != Sheet \u5beb\u5165\u6210\u529f\n- workflow JSON \u672a export \u9032 git\n- N8N_BASE \u5beb\u6b7b ngrok URL"}], "edges": [{"id": "a3013f01fa464e5d", "fromNode": "f2c332b4e1334e1c", "fromSide": "right", "fromEnd": null, "toNode": "3912864296074dce", "toSide": "left", "toEnd": "arrow", "color": null, "label": "LIFF login"}, {"id": "79132e90fa9c4f4b", "fromNode": "f2c332b4e1334e1c", "fromSide": "bottom", "fromEnd": null, "toNode": "8251523d04294e3b", "toSide": "top", "toEnd": "arrow", "color": "4", "label": "POST /orders"}, {"id": "78702863cf844624", "fromNode": "eed41d1d66544f62", "fromSide": "bottom", "fromEnd": null, "toNode": "8251523d04294e3b", "toSide": "right", "toEnd": "arrow", "color": null, "label": "REST \u7ba1\u7406"}, {"id": "a9e26b43e8f44c2b", "fromNode": "eed41d1d66544f62", "fromSide": "bottom", "fromEnd": null, "toNode": "46bd22edd4cb4e3c", "toSide": "top", "toEnd": "arrow", "color": null, "label": "\u76f4\u9023 (service role)"}, {"id": "cdf3d9d6a86c4692", "fromNode": "8251523d04294e3b", "fromSide": "right", "fromEnd": null, "toNode": "46bd22edd4cb4e3c", "toSide": "left", "toEnd": "arrow", "color": "5", "label": "INSERT orders\nn8n_notified=false"}, {"id": "8356ba932e8040a7", "fromNode": "8251523d04294e3b", "fromSide": "bottom", "fromEnd": null, "toNode": "dcdffab941b94f35", "toSide": "top", "toEnd": "arrow", "color": "4", "label": "\u5373\u6642 webhook\n+ secret"}, {"id": "3bd0f65039364b45", "fromNode": "1f49f2acdba645a9", "fromSide": "left", "fromEnd": null, "toNode": "8251523d04294e3b", "toSide": "right", "toEnd": "arrow", "color": "3", "label": "\u88dc\u9001 cron"}, {"id": "860cb17bf67f48bb", "fromNode": "dcdffab941b94f35", "fromSide": "bottom", "fromEnd": null, "toNode": "543d4d754cbf4ebf", "toSide": "top", "toEnd": "arrow", "color": null,